Banker Program. The program offers a unique opportunity to promising
young, motivated people, selected on a competitive basis, to start a
career in ProCredit Bank, to gain thorough theoretical knowledge in
Banking and practical skills. The successful completion of the program
will offer the participants employment at ProCredit Bank.
